commit.message:
Fix typos

Found via `codespell -S po -L crasher,doubleclick`

Fix Message dialog alignment

In e35a3a3 (Fix deprecated initialization, 2020-10-05), the alignment
was changed to fill rather than left align the text labels.  This
results in odd spacing between characters within the words of the label.

Use left alignment for label text in message dialogs.

Fixes #89
Add missing references for defusedxml requirement

Fix compatability with newer meson

Meson 0.60 and newer are completely unable to build revelation without
this fix, due to the deprecation of the positional argument used.

It can be removed without any change to the output.

This is an upstreaming of the patch required to make this build in gentoo:
https://github.com/gentoo/gentoo/commit/3496474bbc48fe59838518b04cf274c5c8b47ae7

Fixes Issue #87

commit.message: Add GitHub Action to check bandit

[BANDIT] Changes to pass bandit checks

- Add .bandit config file
- Use secrets module rather than random for sensitive data
- Remove unused util.execute function
- Remove unused util.random_string function
- Switch from xml.dom.minidom to defusedxml.minidom
- Add #nosec for old unsecure hashes and crypto, required for import/export
- Misc changes including some flake8 changes
Change deprecated gnome-terminal go-to command format
